{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"264087-gaemidul","title":"개미들","description":"개미가 집을 짓는 곳과 먹는 음식을 알고 있습니까? 자세히 알아 보려면 더 읽어보세요.","language":"Korean","langCode":"ko","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Joseph Park"],"illustrators":["Partho Sengupta"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/264087-gaemidul"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/283168/size3/e3c7076c903ab9f82ec702f514a18a25.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/283168/size6/e3c7076c903ab9f82ec702f514a18a25.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279217/size6/32bb690b11f9ca3e62f82be81abeeeda.jpg","text":"니샤는\n할머니와 함께 정원에 갔습니다.\n정원에는 많은 종류의 나무가 있었습니다.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279218/size6/155a1129907c3bc24d723848ce0ef05b.jpg","text":"나무 아래에 개미집이 세워져 있었습니다.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279219/size6/e67c2c08912ddbcec1eb0712b3effd8f.jpg","text":"할머니는 니샤에게 어린 시절에 개미에게 먹이를 주곤했다고 말했습니다. \n니샤는 이것을 듣고 기뻤습니다.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279220/size6/7e802d29c5ece98978590aafddd249d5.jpg","text":"그녀는 집으로 돌아가 상자에서 반죽을 꺼냈습니다.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279221/size6/3198fb7587d3dc38bf79fbeb300eb32c.jpg","text":"다음날 아침, 그녀는 다시 할머니와 함께 정원에 갔습니다. \n그녀는 나무 아래 개미집에 밀가루를 약간 넣었습니다.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279222/size6/f1e4c9950e7ae6d0e460be35f88fca95.jpg","text":"개미들이 밀가루를 먹기 시작했습니다.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279223/size6/ec744053cb4fe150281e3d68cf9f4431.jpg","text":"이것을 보고, 니샤와 할머니는 매우 기뻤습니다.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":7,"words":58}}